.TH "rpcrdma_reset_cwnd" 9 "rpcrdma_reset_cwnd" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
rpcrdma_reset_cwnd \- Reset the xprt's congestion window
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "void" rpcrdma_reset_cwnd
.BI "(struct rpcrdma_xprt *r_xprt "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "r_xprt" 12
controlling transport instance
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Prepare \fIr_xprt\fP for the next connection by reinitializing
its credit grant to one (see RFC 8166, Section 3.3.3).
